{"tid":1091105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司終極敗訴 終院廢「不誠實取用電腦」","createTime":"2019-04-04T02:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:29:44.000Z","uid":246371,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"86c561bc505f03e9acc927bbca70982db1b98c74","tid":1091105,"uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"高院早前就協和小學教師洩露試題案，裁定用自己手機通訊或拍照作案，不能用「不誠實取用電腦」罪檢控，令這條一直被廣泛應用於檢控多種罪行的「萬能key」控罪面臨重大考驗。律政司不服，早前向終審法院終極上訴，堅持使用自己的手機或電腦均屬「取用」，但被法官指詮釋與立法原意相距甚遠。終院今頒下判詞，裁定律政司敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n4名被告是中華基督教會協和小學教師鄭嘉儀、曾詠珊、黃佩雯，及曾的舊同學、於另一間小學任教的余玲菊，4人原審均獲判罪名不成立。律政司先向原審裁判官要求覆核判決，但告失敗，裁判官維持無罪裁決。律政司向高等法院上訴，亦遭法官駁回，維持4人無罪。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：FACC22/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190404&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59447828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190404%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59447828&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvF7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=b1f16813\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190404%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59447828&h=9d507c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190404&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59447828</a>"},{"pid":"fc34ab14f2b2b85b49b205c5c00296abbec64713","tid":1091105,"uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"之前用不誠實取用電腦入罪既人可唔可以上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf58e30e6bf2d0d3ff2d3de5a31790faf1e06855","tid":1091105,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc34ab14f2b2b85b49b205c5c00296abbec64713","tid":1091105,"uid":1550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"之前用不誠實取用電腦入罪既人可唔可以上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"過咗上訴期個堆咪硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" clas